text: Farhat Nadeem Beg from the University of California, San Diego, was named Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2012 for contributions to high intensity laser matter interactions and pulsed power pinches. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:University of California, San Diego faculty Category:Engineers from California Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
